OL,3,COcado axing around 1,000 workers amid
OL,4,Ccost-cutting overhaul
OL,6,FAround 1,000 jobs are being axed at
OL,7,FOcado as the retail technology firm
OL,8,Flooks to slash costs by about #150
OL,9,Fmillion as part of a wider restructure.
OL,11,FThe group confirmed around 5% of its
OL,12,Fglobal workforce is being cut, with
OL,13,Fabout two thirds of the job losses
OL,14,Fimpacting its UK operations.
OL,16,FMost of the UK cuts will affect staff
OL,17,Fat the firm's headquarters in
OL,18,FHatfield, Hertfordshire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
