FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772103930
OL,3,COcado axing around 1,000 workers amid
OL,4,Ccost-cutting overhaul
OL,6,FThe business, which runs robotic
OL,7,Fwarehouses for supermarket chains,
OL,8,Fsaid it plans to scale back research
OL,9,Fand development (R&D), helping it trim
OL,10,Faround #150 million in technology and
OL,11,Fsupport costs in 2026.
OL,13,FThe group also said it will
OL,14,Frestructure its commercial, support
OL,15,Fand R&D operations, which will see
OL,16,FOcado Solutions and Ocado Intelligent
OL,17,FAutomation merged into a single
OL,18,Fdivision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
