OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772103930
OL,3,COcado axing around 1,000 workers amid
OL,4,Ccost-cutting overhaul
OL,6,FOcado chief executive Tim Steiner
OL,7,Fsaid: "Regrettably, this means a
OL,8,Fsignificant number of roles will no
OL,9,Flonger be required.
OL,11,F"We are grateful to colleagues who are
OL,12,Faffected by these changes, and whose
OL,13,Ftalent and hard work have made a
OL,14,Flasting contribution to Ocado. We will
OL,15,Fsupport those impacted through this
OL,16,Fprocess."
